data.description: Wow! Well maintained! This turn-key home is on the market ready for a new buyer to enjoy an open floor plan and lots of room for entertainment. Many upgrades have been completed that includes a brand new roof, new water heater, appliances are only 3 years old, New tile flooring in the bedrooms, AC is 3 years old, new poxy floors in the garage and in the outside patio. As you enter the backyard, you will be welcomed with lots of room for enterainment with a tranquil feeling with outside seating with a nice touch fresh paint along the entire fence. Perfect opportunity to own this lovely home well cared for and near everything! Quick HOA approval. Book your appointment now!
